1 B. The Department shall be the legal successor of and, except
2 as otherwise provided in the Oklahoma Corrections Act of 1967, shall
3 have the powers and duties vested by law in the Office of Management
4 and Enterprise Services in all matters relating to penal
5 institutions, heretofore or hereafter established by the Department,
6 which institutions and community corrections centers shall be under
7 the administrative direction and control of the Department.
8 SECTION 5. REPEALER 57 O.S. 2021, Section 504.7, is
9 hereby repealed.
10 SECTION 6. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
